.SH FILES
.TP
.I midi_input_file
is the output of 
.B textmidi
.
It is a standard MIDI 1.0 file which can be used with programs that play and edit 
standard MIDI 1.0 files.
.
.
.TP
.I output_file
is a text file in the MIDI language supported by 
.B textmidi.
.
.
.TP
.I dynamics.cfg
or other name contains dynamic symbols assigned to MIDI velocities.

.SH CONFORMING TO
International MIDI Association MIDI Specification 1.1.
.SH EXAMPLE
.SH NOTES
